Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.92,0:00:14.89,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\blur1\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.15,0:00:15.73,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.74,0:00:19.04,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies\Nstraight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.29,0:00:22.95,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.96,0:00:26.57,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.58,0:00:30.33,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.34,0:00:33.51,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.88,0:00:36.64,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.64,0:00:40.10,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.18,0:00:44.76,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.77,0:00:48.26,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.27,0:00:50.90,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.99,0:00:54.49,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.66,0:00:59.27,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.28,0:01:02.62,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.43,0:01:34.99,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The secret organization Shocker\Nis plotting world domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.77,0:01:38.75,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This is Shocker's secret base.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.15,0:01:50.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Shocker employs transplants and\Nother techniques out of Nazi Germany
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.86,0:01:55.09,Narrator,,0,0,0,,to create humans amplified with the\Nproperties of insects and animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.14,0:02:07.23,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This is their latest creation:
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.23,0:02:09.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,a human scorpion.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.17,0:02:14.10,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs130\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HFCFFFE&\b1\pos(480.495,236.833)}The Monstrous Scorpion Man
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.45,0:02:17.92,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Countless innocents made to do
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.92,0:02:22.64,Narrator,,0,0,0,,hard labor in this base for\Nthe Scorpion Man experiment
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.64,0:02:27.73,Narrator,,0,0,0,,are to be executed,\Nsimply for collapsing from exhaustion.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.86,0:02:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Fujisawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.12,0:02:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.15,0:02:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,For a failure to qualify
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.29,0:02:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,to become one of\Nour chosen cyborgs,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.63,0:02:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,or even combatants\Nor technicians,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.73,0:02:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,you will all be put to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.88,0:02:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But the great ruler of\Nall, Shocker,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.66,0:02:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,will give you one last chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.35,0:03:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We will now release\Nyou from your cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.67,0:03:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If, within the next ten minutes,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.63,0:03:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,you can pass across the desert\Nand arrive in the safe zone,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.05,0:03:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,we will ensure your freedom,\Nand no further harm will come to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.50,0:03:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Your ten minutes begins now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.80,0:03:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Now... run through the desert.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.35,0:03:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Your lives are on the line!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.66,0:03:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Run...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.27,0:03:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Five minutes have now passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.25,0:03:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Please... take me with you!\NPlease!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.28,0:04:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Nine minutes have passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.16,0:04:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We will now begin the countdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.51,0:04:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.01,0:04:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Six.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.57,0:04:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Five.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.32,0:04:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Four.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.83,0:04:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Three.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.37,0:04:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Two.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.68,0:04:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,One.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.73,0:04:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Their sentence will be carried\Nout by man-eating scorpions.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.81,0:04:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Let man-eating scorpions\Ncarry out the death sentence!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.50,0:04:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What did we do wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.79,0:04:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell us!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.17,0:04:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.43,0:04:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, I don't want to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.16,0:04:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Spare us!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.22,0:04:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, spare us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.36,0:05:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What an awful thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.02,0:05:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,How can they be so merciless?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.39,0:05:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.69,0:05:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The man-eating scorpions, a proud\Ninvention by our Shocker scientists,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.89,0:05:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,have passed the\Nhuman trial stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.30,0:05:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Their completion will deliver\Nthe Earth into Shocker's hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.36,0:05:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Scorpion Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.66,0:05:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Execute Operation M1 at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.38,0:05:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Then destroy Hongo Takeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.72,0:06:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.75,0:06:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Killing that man is my\Nlone purpose in life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.95,0:06:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,First,\NI will set some bait for Hongo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.84,0:06:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That old man, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.73,0:06:17.54,Narrator,,0,0,0,,At that same time, Hongo Takeshi\Nwas working with Tachibana Tobei,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.54,0:06:22.23,Narrator,,0,0,0,,his supporter, assistant, and\Ntrainer, to test his cyborg prowess.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.24,0:06:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,15.30 meters!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.06,0:06:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,48.70 meters!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.18,0:06:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.37,0:06:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Look at that\Ndestructive power!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.74,0:07:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo's superpowers definitely come\Nfrom that wind turbine in his belt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.83,0:07:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the source of\Nyour superhuman abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.89,0:07:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It appears so.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.72,0:07:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The wind spins the dynamo,\Nwhich builds up energy,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.41,0:07:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,which is transferred to\Nmy enhanced musculature.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.26,0:07:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's utterly incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.46,0:07:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You've always had exceptional\Nreflexes and stamina.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.23,0:07:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Those traits have been artificially\Nenhanced, giving you unfathomable power.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.18,0:07:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,With training,\Nyou could likely grow even stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.32,0:07:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.98,0:07:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Strange news came in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.66,0:07:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Strange news?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.20,0:07:47.83,Narrator,,0,0,0,,To repeat that last story,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.83,0:07:51.99,Narrator,,0,0,0,,ten bodies found adrift off\Nthe coast of the Boso Peninsula
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.99,0:07:53.91,Narrator,,0,0,0,,disappeared immediately\Nafter discovery.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.91,0:07:58.97,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The local Nagahama Police believe\Nthat a fishing boat capsized,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.97,0:08:03.47,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and the disappearance was the result\Nof long-term weathering at sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.47,0:08:05.24,Narrator,,0,0,0,,but the Coast Guard\Nhas received no report
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.24,0:08:08.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,of any such vessels capsizing\Nover the last few months...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.83,0:08:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Could Shocker be behind this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.71,0:08:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.85,0:08:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to go to Nagahama.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.39,0:08:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Hongo, take me with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.58,0:08:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you killed my\Nfather, and I hated you for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.22,0:08:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But now that I know it was really\Nthat awful organization, Shocker...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.44,0:08:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to help you, to make up for the\Ntrouble I've caused you in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.39,0:08:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not a wise idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.78,0:08:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,If anything were to happen to\Nyou, your late father...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.14,0:08:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I believe he'd allow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.15,0:08:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.00,0:08:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Hongo...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.98,0:08:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Tachibana, I'm leaving now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.53,0:08:56.71,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H559BA9&\c&H2E3D42&}Chiba Prefecture Nagahama Police Station
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.40,0:09:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go! They'll kill me!\NThey'll kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.24,0:09:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone save me! Save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.34,0:09:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll kill me!\NThey'll kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.97,0:09:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He was babbling about "Shocker"\Nbeing behind the recent incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.77,0:09:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.98,0:09:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was that old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.22,0:09:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He apparently escaped\Nfrom a mental institution.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.96,0:09:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Some men from their\Nstaff came to fetch him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.66,0:09:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He seems pretty convinced they'll\Nkill or experiment on him...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.01,0:09:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Please... let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.12,0:09:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.55,0:09:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't talk to anyone!\NSpare me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.82,0:09:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.30,0:09:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.54,0:09:50.70,Narrator,,0,0,0,,When wind spins the turbine in\Ncyborg Hongo Takeshi's belt,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.70,0:09:52.94,Narrator,,0,0,0,,he transforms into\Nthe Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.09,0:10:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.17,0:10:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Attention, Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.22,0:10:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be taking that\Nvaluable witness with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.43,0:11:31.74,Bumper Episode 2-13,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355,520)\blur1}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.46,0:11:33.93,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,It will be dawn soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.76,0:11:40.24,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,Shocker wants to destroy this\Npeaceful town and its people,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.24,0:11:42.49,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,and bend all of\Nsociety to their whims.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.32,0:11:46.38,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,Nobody knows about the evil\Nthey get up to in secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.98,0:11:48.58,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,They wouldn't believe\Nme if I told them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.06,0:11:50.70,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,That is why I must fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.77,0:11:53.74,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,This poor old man is just\None of those I must save.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.74,0:11:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.\NI don't know anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.75,0:11:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Ito.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.58,0:12:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to hang in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.50,0:12:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Ito.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.55,0:12:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The lights! Turn on the lights!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.91,0:12:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.09,0:12:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.22,0:12:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.48,0:12:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayase?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.63,0:12:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go already, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.96,0:13:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayase!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.70,0:13:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey... What brings you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.87,0:13:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.14,0:13:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's been a\Nwhile, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.28,0:13:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought him here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.75,0:13:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss told me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.40,0:13:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ruriko...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.53,0:13:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Tachibana told you to?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.95,0:13:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are these people?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.97,0:13:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.66,0:13:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Hayase Goro.\NHe's my best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.20,0:13:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is Midorikawa Ruriko.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.28,0:13:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ruriko's father was\Nalso killed by Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.76,0:13:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll help you out from now on.\NNo matter what you need, Hongo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.15,0:13:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel a lot better\Nhaving you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.71,0:13:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me introduce you, Ruriko.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.07,0:13:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This man is my racing rival,\Nand also my best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.40,0:13:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He calls me his rival, but on race\Ndays, he always beats me by a nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.58,0:13:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I got so frustrated, I went away for\Na while to learn some new techniques.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.89,0:13:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Ito.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.78,0:14:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,There are all these\Npeople here for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.47,0:14:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, take heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.66,0:14:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You're safe, Mr. Ito.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.26,0:14:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't let these Shocker\Nguys lay one finger on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.24,0:14:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I see that now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.21,0:14:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.62,0:14:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Scorpions!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.31,0:14:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay in this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.93,0:14:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.14,0:14:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.93,0:14:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.19,0:15:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope those two are all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.88,0:15:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy they're\Nfighting is merciless.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.96,0:15:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure they'll be\Nfine, Mr. Ito.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.74,0:15:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,A scorpion!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.75,0:15:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The terrible\Nman-eating scorpions!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.89,0:15:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Man-eating scorpions?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.87,0:15:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,My dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.23,0:15:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Ito!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.39,0:16:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.30,0:16:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Ito!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.03,0:16:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ruriko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.03,0:16:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.46,0:16:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo!\NThey took Ruriko in a car!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.08,0:16:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go after them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.73,0:16:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.03,0:17:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayase, should we take them?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.51,0:17:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.37,0:17:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If we just tail them,\Nwe might learn where Shocker's base is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.71,0:17:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.81,0:18:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell us where Hongo is!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.22,0:18:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Hongo?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.38,0:18:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,How should I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.38,0:18:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk or you die!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.66,0:18:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayase... go save Ruriko!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.27,0:18:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.97,0:18:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,All right... Shocker combatants\Nnever act without a commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.63,0:18:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is your Shocker commander?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.78,0:18:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayase...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.93,0:18:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Hongo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.51,0:18:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayase Goro is no\Nlonger my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.99,0:18:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I am now Scorpion Man,\Na Shocker commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.34,0:19:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.59,0:19:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I joined Shocker of\Nmy own free will.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.73,0:19:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I allowed them to alter me
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.87,0:19:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,so that I could\Nfinally beat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.00,0:19:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And now at last, I have won!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.34,0:19:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Look there, Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.07,0:19:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayase...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.51,0:19:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do whatever\Nit takes to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.63,0:19:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon, Hongo...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.07,0:19:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll learn the might of\Nthe man-eating scorpions!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.44,0:19:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.06,0:19:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.43,0:20:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Get them!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.08,0:20:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hide. Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.09,0:20:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayase, stop this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.84,0:20:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Snap out of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.83,0:20:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to\Nfight my best friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.23,0:20:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.34,0:20:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayase!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.89,0:20:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll say this just once...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.52,0:20:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Return to the man you once were!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.47,0:22:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Scissors!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.17,0:23:21.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The terrifying man-eating scorpions\Nvanished when Scorpion Man did.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.84,0:23:26.27,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But Shocker was honing its\Nclaws for another strike.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.02,0:23:33.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What fate awaits Takeshi and Ruriko,\Nhis friend and new assistant?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.04,0:23:40.80,Cont,,0,0,150,,{\blur.8\fad(0,450)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.12,0:23:42.89,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs67.5\fnCalibri\pos(499.031,496.481)}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.90,0:23:46.40,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The next assassin Shocker\NHQ sends for our Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.40,0:23:48.36,Narrator,,0,0,0,,is the man-eating Sarracenian.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.74,0:23:51.99,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What horrors will this man transformed\Ninto a carnivorous plant bring to bear?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.32,0:23:54.19,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Shocker lashes out with a\Nnew, eerie plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.19,0:23:56.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Fight on, Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.10,0:23:57.99,Narrator,,0,0,0,,See you next week\Nfor more Kamen Rider,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.99,0:24:01.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,in "The Man-Eating Sarracenian."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.92,0:24:10.76,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,He came here on a storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.34,0:24:13.34,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is he? Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.35,0:24:15.30,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is this man of storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.31,0:24:18.35,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,who sends the\Nvillains scattering?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.85,0:24:20.72,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.73,0:24:22.59,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,His mask stands for justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.60,0:24:24.39,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Start it up! Rev it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.40,0:24:25.73,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Get that engine running!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.19,0:24:28.23,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Give me top speed, Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.28,0:24:33.94,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Hit them with\Nall of your anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.95,0:24:37.53,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Put an end to Shocker's evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.54,0:24:41.12,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider! Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.62,0:24:45.38,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!